        <mxCell id="3KkN48R1lRXVecXf_ZRn-4" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Describing Relationship betwreen&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;tables very Important for&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt; &quot;Reporting and Analytics&quot;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Differnt types of relationships we have&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;gt; 1 to 1&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;gt; 1 to Many&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Here Star Schema Relationship is:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;In star schema, the relationship between fact and dimension is 1-to-many(1:N)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
